cumulpdppixelwise -> cumulative + median pdp plot 
lcr cumul -> lcr, dcr, lcr - dcr cumul plot
pdp_heatmap -> heat map of pdp
pdpvsdcr -> pdp vs ln(dcr) (each data point is from different bias)
roipdp -> check cumulative pdp from the heatmap for a region of interest

lighton -> subfile to get spad counts from data file
photonflux -> subfile to get incident photon flux from calib file and Hamamatsu ref
